data.description: This inviting home, nestled in the sought-after Walker Place subdivision, offers a seamless blend of comfort and convenience. Situated on a corner lot, it boasts easy access to HWY 190 and the business 190 bypass, making commuting a breeze. Nearby amenities include the South Park Public Pool, playground, and the esteemed Martin Walker Elementary School. The residence features a spacious open-concept layout with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and a versatile office space that could be used as a 4th bedroom. The master suite impresses with a garden tub, separate shower, and a sizable walk-in closet, complemented by direct access to the back patio. The well-appointed kitchen seamlessly flows into the living room, complete with a cozy fireplace and elegant crown molding. Tile flooring throughout ensures both style and practicality. Equipped with modern conveniences like a sprinkler system and alarm, this home is ready to welcome its new owners.
